Look at this ornament in the car.

38
00:03:18,780 --> 00:03:19,740
You should be familiar with it, right?

39
00:03:21,780 --> 00:03:23,460
My uncle gave it to my dad.

40
00:03:25,380 --> 00:03:26,060
