112
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:17,420
Who are you?

113
00:08:17,620 --> 00:08:18,900
Why are you in my house?

114
00:08:19,420 --> 00:08:20,700
My mom took me here.

115
00:08:21,180 --> 00:08:22,380
Are you my brother

116
00:08:22,380 --> 00:08:23,460
