117
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:27,900
How about I give you a tour of my house?

118
00:08:28,100 --> 00:08:28,740
Okay.

119
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:37,980
Honglin,

120
00:08:38,940 --> 00:08:40,140
