212
00:15:49,980 --> 00:15:50,540
It's okay.

213
00:15:50,660 --> 00:15:51,980
With you, there's double security.

214
00:15:52,380 --> 00:15:53,100
Be good.

215
00:15:53,100 --> 00:15:54,380
He suddenly left the office

216
00:15:54,380 --> 00:15:55,140
