224
00:16:29,020 --> 00:16:29,740
Here, take it.

225
00:16:32,540 --> 00:16:34,020
I came here today

226
00:16:34,140 --> 00:16:35,020
to tell you something.

227
00:16:37,380 --> 00:16:38,380
