336
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:27,350
♪You ask if shooting stars have secrets♪

337
00:27:27,990 --> 00:27:31,190
♪Is the moon pretending to be awake?♪

338
00:27:31,190 --> 00:27:34,900
♪Just like me, just like you,
